subject: Gymnastics
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The Michigan senior Sam Mikulak, who on Friday won the all-around title, earned a record-tying seventh individual N.C.A.A. gymnastics title with a victory on the parallel bars in Ann Arbor, Mich.
